  (text "Changes for NPN GE\n1) Q1 Q2 changed from PNP CBE to NPN EBC format (AC128 to AC130)\n2) -9V becomes 9V\n3) shoot for 120 hfe for Q2,    80 hfe for Q1.\n4) Adjust q2 collector voltage to 4.5-5V\n\n\n"
